    public class TransactionDistSQLStatementBaseVisitor<T>
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
implements TransactionDistSQLStatementVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of TransactionDistSQLStatementVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
